data.text: I am Gonzalo, an avid underground music listener, and I’ve decided to share my love of music with everyone through this blog. This blog dedicated to supporting and showing the world new and upcoming bands in the genres of Emo, Punk, Hardcore, Shoegaze, Powerviolence and everything in between. Check daily for new bands and other music related news.
